{"data":{"page":{"id":"5413e8a1-7ee6-59cd-8239-15ef3b08f5cd","html":"<p>While working at WCRS, I was asked to build an animated responsive HTML Artemis ad for the iPad. This ad was displayed in the Times and Sunday websites. I used the libraries <a href=\"http://spritely.net/\">spritely</a> and <a href=\"http://ricostacruz.com/jquery.transit/\">transit</a> to create the sequence of animated sprites and the CSS3 animations.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/d797cdaa56e207c403f1d85188f0088d/877ff/1.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.7%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/d797cdaa56e207c403f1d85188f0088d/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/d797cdaa56e207c403f1d85188f0088d/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/d797cdaa56e207c403f1d85188f0088d/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<video class=\"full-img\" style=\"border: 1px solid #CCC; border-radius: 30px;\" width=\"100%\" controls>\n    <source src=\"/artemis-profit-hunter-627b00004f5786aeb184ba36a65b8cb9.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\" />\n</video>\n<p>I was also involved in several content updates for the Artemis website and newsletter.</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/3